  "description": "A warrior from the source of the springs, and a tribal guardian that patrols the waters and shores.\nThese warriors always lead the charge, and the swords in their hands are as teeth that saw through bone. The members of the tribe who practice the sword do so in the water, honing their skill and strength against the resistance of the water itself. The best among them can cleave a swimming fish in two.",
